pokemonhotel

Class Setup

  • java.lang.Object
    • pokemonhotel.Setup

  • public class Setup
extends java.lang.Object
    An object of the class Setup holds all the information on the pokemons, assistants and hotel rooms it creates. This info is store in both array lists and hash maps for later retrieval.
